HOW IT'S MADE
-----------------------

- Download Zig from official site. (No installation required).

- Get the Release of 'zig-regex' from https://github.com/zig-utils/zig-regex, 
  place to "zig-regex" subfolder. (Remove old files).

- If required, the "ZigRegexWorker.zig" file can be edited in Visual Studio Code or any editor.

- To build, execute:

    > build.cmd

  (If "zig.exe" is not in PATH, "build.cmd" can be adjusted to include the path).

  It will create the "ZigRegexWorker.exe" file.

- Commit the changes (including "ZigRegexWorker.exe") to Git.

- Build the main Visual Studio solution.

